    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required gradation levels. The single gap (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is acknowledged and accepted given that the single F1717 configuration is the standard regulatory comparator and multi-condition testing is not required by the applicable guidance. All three QoIs satisfy E/uval < 1.96. Overall credibility is sufficient to support the Medium assurance level for this Class II device submission. Package is submitted under ProfileMinimal; digital signature is pending completion of the institutional signature workflow and will be appended prior to final regulatory submission.",
